Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used\Nas a hint for reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the\Nmost mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta's the lead actor today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He might not be all that reliable as a friend,\Nbut we're all following him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.74,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teitan Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody, dig in!\NI don't want to see any picky eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A teenage boy eating\Nwith grade-school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Personally,\NI'm enjoying the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Growing up in the States, everybody\Nhelped themselves at the school cafeteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I usually ended up\Neating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's intriguing how Japanese schools\Nfoster a sense of community.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, this was fun\Nthe first time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nyou left your carrots again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm just saving\Nthem for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's always somebody who picks out\Nthe vegetables he doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:48.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's always a dumb guy who brags\Nabout being the fastest eater in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course, in this class,\Nit's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I'm number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He beat Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},\NI'm not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go down\Nto the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} left most\Nof his lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!\NYou know him and food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nhasn't played with us for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's been going\Nstraight home after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe an upperclassman\Nis bullying him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Genta's not the kind\Nof guy who'd get bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if he was,\Nhe'd be safer sticking with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a problem\Nwith his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone in\Nhis family is gravely ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or his parents\Nare fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't do anything\Nabout death or divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents are fine!\NThey're still happily running their liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried, so I dropped by\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house yesterday to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nis afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents told me he was shivering\Ninside his futon the moment he got home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept getting, "It's nothing",\Nno matter how many times I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he might\Ntell his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me\Nif he opens up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nbehind our backs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you practicing\Nto become a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! You skipped lunch\Nto slim down for ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this cool ninja flick\Nthe other day and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why were you shivering\Nunder the covers at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a nightmare about\Nbeing attacked by a bloody samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you're training to\Nfight your imaginary enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I... The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My life is in danger!\NA hitman's out to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a hitman want\Nto kill an elementary school kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right... Unless it was me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was dumb\Nto tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Ntell us the whole story!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking through that\Ntunnel under the train tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I heard these\Nfootsteps behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see\Nanything in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I stopped, he'd stop,\Nand when I ran, he ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably just the echo of your\Nfootsteps against the tunnel wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, somebody pushed me\Ndown the stairs on the overpass,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and yesterday a motorbike\Nran a red light and almost hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big bolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could it\Nhave fallen from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's from that\Ndepartment store sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bolt just happened\Nto rust out, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just having a bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, maybe you should go to a shrine\Nand have them do a purifying ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... This was more\Nthan just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cord on this neon sign\Nwas cut with a sharp object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone deliberately cut it before\Nloosening the bolt, to drop the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, maybe it was just a crazy guy\Nattacking anybody who passed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I think there\Nwas a specific target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the Kamen Yaiba capsule machine\NGenta's always drooling over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then he really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like Genta's life\Nreally {\i1}is{\i0} in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell us\Neverything, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you a target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the serial snatcher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crook who's been snatching bags\Nfrom old people and unsuspecting women?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... About a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see the wanted\Nposters until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They asked where I'd seen\Nthe guy on the posters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and by that time I'd forgotten\Nwhere I saw the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I saw a guy\Nwho saw the snatcher with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five days ago, the snatcher\Nattacked a woman by my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I dropped by\Nthe crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw\Nhim in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blond guy who was near me\Nwhen I saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grabbed him by the hand\Nand took him to the nearest cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the guy said he didn't\Nremember me or the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nhe was the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When I saw the snatcher,\NI think that guy was sitting near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he must've\Nseen the snatcher too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was really sleepy then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I swear that\Nblond guy was nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was there too.\NOr maybe he wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you'd get\Nsleepy after sitting down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A movie theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or inside a train...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the look of things, the blond guy is probably\Nworking with the person targeting Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. Why didn't you tell\Nthe police you were in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I got a phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you say anything about me, you're dead!\NAnd your friends and family too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you didn't\Ntell anybody until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is going\Nfrom bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knows your phone number,\Nhe must know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we went\Nto the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the snatcher might think\NGenta remembered something,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there's no telling\Nwhat he'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might even be spying\Non us this very minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember anything\Nthat might help us look for the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told the cops,\Nbut he was smoking a cigarette with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the snatcher\Nis left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was wearing\Na weird T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was black with\Na skull and numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one! That one!\NIt was just like that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the snatcher\Nwho's after Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. He doesn't look\Nlike the guy I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher's T-shirt\Ndidn't say "1999".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "202"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember\Nwhere you got that T-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shop by the train station\Ncalled Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThe skull shirt is an original from our shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've put out a lot of versions,\Nbut I don't remember one that said "202".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What other versions are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"1999", "HELP", "ESCAPE"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of dangerous-sounding words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember back in 1999,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when everyone was talking about\Nend-of-the-millennium prophecies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we\Ndid a 1999 shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any suspicious-looking\Npeople buying those T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno. It's been a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really remember\Nall our customers' faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} could at least remember\Nwhere he saw the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could try movie theaters\Nand trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. You can't smoke\Nin those places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! You must've gotten sleepy\Nfrom eating too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy\Nwasn't eating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching him\Nthe whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I just remember him reading\Na newspaper and smoking a cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come you can remember all that,\Nbut not where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't he get annoyed at you\Nfor staring at him for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, our eyes never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's where they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The skull T-shirt\Nwith the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And a place where your eyes\Nwould never meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and you wouldn't attract attention\Nfor staring at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got it, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The very place\Nyou saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The optician's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where you\Nsaw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said he didn't get upset\Neven though you were staring at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't see you staring at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he'd taken his glasses off\Nto have them fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never been\Nto an optician's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's got to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nit'd also have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?\NI thought I'd cracked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself\Nthe modern-day Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.\NEven a genius makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't feel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me if you remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:15:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could it be?\NThe place Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you can stare at somebody\Nwithout getting in trouble, and also get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's school!\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} always falls asleep there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the snatcher was at our school,\Nwe'd have seen him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never stop eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to put on weight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?\NI like to snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got ice cream on your face,\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you remember something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three chicken and four liver, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just have\Nsome ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,French food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show some self-control!\NYou're almost home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red... White... Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NThat's the French flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the colors\Nred, white and blue anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s always wearing a red bowtie,\Nwhite shirt and blue jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is he the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\NWould Conan do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but the colors\Nred, white and blue keep spinning in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget\Nto go straight home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get any fatter,\Neven the piggies will laugh at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ayumi,\Ncalling me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not that fat, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!\NIt was back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seventh floor of\Nthe building above the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop! Hold that elevator!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which floor, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The s-seventh floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're that blond... guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about forgetting you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered where it was!\NWhere you and me saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could be\Nlistening in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you remember too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk it over\Nbefore we go to the cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make sure we've got\Nour stories straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere safe\Nfrom other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I think the name he wrote\Nin our schedule book was Someda...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't knock off\Nthe accusations, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A T-shirt with a skull\Nand the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder the police couldn't\Npin down the snatcher's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta was looking at your\Nreflection in a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the kids from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you never got angry at Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nfor staring at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he was watching you\Nin the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "202" he saw written\Non your T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was actually "SOS"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the left hand\Nwas really your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where Genta would go that has\Na mirror in front of the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and where he could get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the barber shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta didn't realize you and\Nthe snatcher were the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you had your hair\Nbleached while he was napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guy with a black hair and glasses\Nchanged into a blond guy without glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Genta didn't see your clothes\Nbecause they were covered with a smock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He misremembered you\Nas two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about,\Nyou little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eyewitness\Nstanding right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber who\Ndyed your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been lucky until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As it happens,\Nthe barber doesn't watch TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the police haven't posted\Nyour picture in his neighborhood yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dyed your hair black with coloring\Nthat could be washed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you thought\Nno one would recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the police got the snatcher's fingerprints\Noff the last bag he tried to snatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If those prints match yours,\Nyou can't talk your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what was this kid\Ndoing back in this neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luring you here,\Nthat's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had him get ice cream on his face\Nthat looked like shaving cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stare at the French flag, which is\Nred, white and blue like a barber pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he stared\Nat his reflection...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like he was looking\Nin a barber's mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We knew all along\Nthat you were following us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we convinced Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nto play dumb—no difficult task—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and lure you into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids think\Nyou can mess with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing,\Nyou old broad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really think I'd walk all over town\Njust to lure you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NLook around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Genta bought us some time,\Nwe made a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is\Nswarming with cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's how the\Nsnatcher got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe the words\Ncoming out of your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really a grade-schooler,\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just imitating\Nthe detectives on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge victory for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're so lazy, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you totally fell asleep\Nwhile the snatcher was having his hair dyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber said he didn't wake me up\Nbecause I looked so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess they say sleep\Nis good for growing kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were right\Nand the criminal wasn't really left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty sure it wasn't {\i1}him{\i0},\Nsince he'd target me before Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it did shake me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know?\NThen here's another factoid for your files.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin is left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:08.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wanted to see\Nwhat was inside this attaché case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the key\Nis still in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.98,0:24:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:35.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.87,0:24:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cellular phone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.87,0:24:45.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.87,0:24:42.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:45.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How could the great Kogoro Mouri—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.00,0:24:45.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
